de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces.textobjects

Interface ITextObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IErpsData, ITextObjectInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextObject

    public interface ITextObject
extends ITextObjectInfo
    The text objects are predefined as a forms that are inserted into the text to improve the processing time.
